import { Icon } from "@iconify/react";
import {
  Timeline,
  TimelineConnector,
  TimelineContent,
  TimelineDot,
  TimelineItem,
  TimelineOppositeContent,
  TimelineSeparator,
} from "@mui/lab";
import FrostlineGames from "./frostline-games";
import MarmaraUniversity from "./marmara-universitesi";
import TrustFi from "./trustfi";
import Echonos from "./echonos";
import Elyapim from "./elyapim";
import Acarnet from "./acarnet";
import { Button, Container, Stack, Typography } from "@mui/material";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

export default function ExperienceTimeline() {
  return (
    <Container
      maxWidth="fluid"
      sx={{ backgroundColor: "#0D0D0D", pt: 15, pb: 15 }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Stack
          direction="row"
          alignItems="center"
          justifyContent="center"
          mb={5}
        >
          <Typography
            variant="h4"
            gutterBottom
            color="white"
            textAlign="center"
            sx={{
              background:
                "linear-gradient(primary,primary) left 0 bottom 10% /100% 20% no-repeat",
            }}
          >
            Experience
          </Typography>
        </Stack>
        <Timeline position="alternate">
          <TimelineItem>
            <TimelineOppositeContent
              sx={{ m: "auto 0" }}
              align="right"
              variant="body2"
              color="white"
            >
              Full-Stack Developer
            </TimelineOppositeContent>
            <TimelineSeparator>
              <TimelineConnector />
              <TimelineDot color="primary">
                <Icon icon="ic:twotone-developer-mode" />
              </TimelineDot>
              <TimelineConnector />
            </TimelineSeparator>
            <TimelineContent sx={{ py: "12px", px: 2 }}>
              <FrostlineGames />
            </TimelineContent>
          </TimelineItem>
          <TimelineItem>
            <TimelineOppositeContent
              sx={{ m: "auto 0" }}
              variant="body2"
              color="white"
            >
              Software Engineer Intern
            </TimelineOppositeContent>
            <TimelineSeparator>
              <TimelineConnector />
              <TimelineDot color="primary">
                <Icon icon="ic:twotone-developer-mode" />
              </TimelineDot>
              <TimelineConnector />
            </TimelineSeparator>
            <TimelineContent sx={{ py: "12px", px: 2 }}>
              <MarmaraUniversity />
            </TimelineContent>
          </TimelineItem>
          <TimelineItem>
            <TimelineOppositeContent
              sx={{ m: "auto 0" }}
              variant="body2"
              color="white"
            >
              Graphic Designer
            </TimelineOppositeContent>
            <TimelineSeparator>
              <TimelineConnector />
              <TimelineDot color="primary">
                <Icon icon="icon-park-outline:graphic-design-two" />
              </TimelineDot>
              <TimelineConnector />
            </TimelineSeparator>
            <TimelineContent sx={{ py: "12px", px: 2 }}>
              <TrustFi />
            </TimelineContent>
          </TimelineItem>
          <TimelineItem>
            <TimelineOppositeContent
              sx={{ m: "auto 0" }}
              variant="body2"
              color="white"
            >
              Junior Software Developer
            </TimelineOppositeContent>
            <TimelineSeparator>
              <TimelineConnector />
              <TimelineDot color="primary">
                <Icon icon="ic:twotone-developer-mode" />
              </TimelineDot>
              <TimelineConnector />
            </TimelineSeparator>
            <TimelineContent sx={{ py: "12px", px: 2 }}>
              <Echonos />
            </TimelineContent>
          </TimelineItem>
          <TimelineItem>
            <TimelineOppositeContent
              sx={{ m: "auto 0" }}
              variant="body2"
              color="white"
            >
              Web Designer
            </TimelineOppositeContent>
            <TimelineSeparator>
              <TimelineConnector />
              <TimelineDot color="primary">
                <Icon icon="ic:baseline-computer" />
              </TimelineDot>
              <TimelineConnector />
            </TimelineSeparator>
            <TimelineContent sx={{ py: "12px", px: 2 }}>
              <Elyapim />
            </TimelineContent>
          </TimelineItem>
          <TimelineItem>
            <TimelineOppositeContent
              sx={{ m: "auto 0" }}
              variant="body2"
              color="white"
            >
              Web Designer
            </TimelineOppositeContent>
            <TimelineSeparator>
              <TimelineConnector />
              <TimelineDot color="primary">
                <Icon icon="ic:baseline-computer" />
              </TimelineDot>
              <TimelineConnector />
            </TimelineSeparator>
            <TimelineContent sx={{ py: "12px", px: 2 }}>
              <Acarnet />
            </TimelineContent>
          </TimelineItem>
        </Timeline>{" "}
        <Stack justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" width="100%" mt={10}>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            size="large"
            component={Link}
            to={"../experience"}
            sx={{
              backgroundColor: "primary",
              color: "black",
              textTransform: "capitalize",
              borderRadius: 2,
              width: 150,
            }}
          >
            See More
          </Button>
        </Stack>
      </Container>
    </Container>
  );
}
